headline: Mitratech Unveils Premier Partner Awards, Honoring Industry Leaders Driving AI Innovation & Compliance Excellence
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, Sept. 16, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Mitratech, a global compliance and automation technology company for nearly four decades, and now a global leader in agentic AI, today announced the winners of its inaugural Premier Partner Awards at the HR Technology Conference & Exposition (HR Tech) 2025 in Las Vegas.
